80
00:06:58,785 --> 00:07:02,277
- I wanna see him. He'll feel better.
- lsabelle, not right now.

81
00:07:02,455 --> 00:07:04,946
Let him meet with the doctor
for a while, okay?

82
00:07:07,260 --> 00:07:08,727
Sorry.

83
00:07:08,895 --> 00:07:11,989
This is my daughter lsabelle.
Isabelle, this is Tom Baldwin.

84
00:07:12,165 --> 00:07:14,497
- Hi.
- Shawn told me about you.

85
00:07:14,667 --> 00:07:15,793
Hi.

86
00:07:18,538 --> 00:07:19,869
Hi.

87
00:07:23,643 --> 00:07:26,407
You're staring at me. Why?

88
00:07:28,848 --> 00:07:30,713
How is he?

89
