But you did see Shawn Farrell
on Tuesday?

175
00:12:34,687 --> 00:12:38,384
A home loan from the center.
And how did the meeting end?

176
00:12:39,592 --> 00:12:43,688
Oh, well, congratulations.
That's a really nice neighborhood.

177
00:12:45,030 --> 00:12:46,964
No, no, Mister Donavan.
Thanks for your time.

178
00:12:47,133 --> 00:12:50,398
We'll be in touch
if we need anything further.

179
00:12:51,637 --> 00:12:53,798
You know, your nephew is one
of the leaders of the center.

180
00:12:53,973 --> 00:12:55,770
He sees dozens of 4400s every day.

181
00:12:55,941 --> 00:12:59,104
And the ones that we've spoken to
who have registered abilities with us,

182
00:12:59,278 --> 00:13:01,542
they have minor stuff.
Nothing like the capacity

183
00:13:01,714 --> 00:13:03,181
to induce insanity.

184
00:13:03,349 --> 00:13:05,408
And that's assuming
that whoever did this

185
00:13:05,584 --> 00:13:07,711
had to be in proximity to Shawn
to make it happen.

186
00:13:07,887 --> 00:13:09,081
Whoever?

187
00:13:09,255 --> 00:13:11,849
We basically know who did this.
It was Daniel Armand.

188
00:13:12,024 --> 00:13:13,719
Either he did it, or he gave the order.

189
00:13:13,893 --> 00:13:16,453
Well, no, the truth is we don't actually
know that Shawn's condition

190
00:13:16,629 --> 00:13:18,119
is the result of an attack.

191
00:13:18,297 --> 00:13:20,527
Nova's not claiming credit,

192
00:13:20,699 --> 00:13:24,100
and Shawn's exactly the right age
for onset of schizophrenia.

193
00:13:24,270 --> 00:13:26,067
So it's possible
that we're looking for a crime,

194
00:13:26,238 --> 00:13:28,206
and the only thing
we're gonna find is a tragedy.

195
00:13:29,775 --> 00:13:31,402
Then there's nothing we can do.

196
00:13:35,214 --> 00:13:36,374
I cannot accept that.

197
00:13:36,549 --> 00:13:38,244
Nova threatened Shawn.
Shawn got sick.

198
00:13:38,417 --> 00:13:41,978
For right now,
that's all the cause and effect I need.

199
00:13:49,762 --> 00:13:50,922
You're Zachary?

200
00:13:51,096 --> 00:13:53,326
- Thanks for meeting me out here.
- It's all right.

201
00:13:53,499 --> 00:13:56,525
Matthew said you had something
you wanted to discuss.

202
00:13:57,136 --> 00:13:59,536
About six weeks ago,
a friend of mine from quarantine,

203
00:13:59,705 --> 00:14:02,799
she asked me to meet her
for dinner.

204
00:14:02,975 --> 00:14:07,378
So I go, and she's asking me
all sorts of questions.

205
00:14:07,546 --> 00:14:09,844
Now, she never came right out
and said it,

206
00:14:10,015 --> 00:14:13,883
but I swear she was feeling me out
to see if I would join the Nova Group.

207
00:14:14,053 --> 00:14:15,782
She was recruiting you?

208
00:14:16,422 --> 00:14:18,947
I mean, she used to bitch
about the government all the time.

209
00:14:19,124 --> 00:14:21,888
- I guess she just finally got fed up.
- Zachary.

210
00:14:22,061 --> 00:14:24,529
If you got a name, give it to me.

211
00:14:27,967 --> 00:14:29,559
Jane Nance.

212
00:14:31,103 --> 00:14:33,333
Thank you for coming forward.

213
00:14:42,381 --> 00:14:43,905
Hi.

214
00:14:48,888 --> 00:14:50,378
Todd?

215
00:14:52,858 --> 00:14:55,554
Ms. Mareva. What's up?

216
00:14:55,728 --> 00:14:59,129
Those things you said about me.
They're very private.

217
00:15:00,032 --> 00:15:01,226
How did you know?

218
00:15:02,935 --> 00:15:05,563
Sometimes, when I'm talking
to somebody,

219
00:15:05,738 --> 00:15:10,471
if they feel something real strong,
I feel it too.

220
00:15:11,877 --> 00:15:15,438
And then I know
why they feel that way.

221
00:15:15,614 --> 00:15:16,603
I see it.

222
00:15:17,549 --> 00:15:22,509
So you saw what happened
to my family?

223
00:15:22,688 --> 00:15:26,021
Not the whole thing.
I just get, like, fragments.

224
00:15:27,927 --> 00:15:30,896
I saw the two cars hit.
I saw this guy.

225
00:15:31,063 --> 00:15:33,588
There were empty beer bottles
by his seat.

226
00:15:33,766 --> 00:15:35,757
He thought about getting out.

227
00:15:36,869 --> 00:15:38,996
Calling the cops.

228
00:15:39,972 --> 00:15:41,200
I guess he changed his mind.

229
00:15:41,874 --> 00:15:46,038
The man who hit them,
you know who he is?

230
00:15:46,211 --> 00:15:48,805
Yeah, I already wrote it down.

231
00:15:49,782 --> 00:15:51,773
